Class TreeNode<K extends java.lang.Comparable<? super K>,V>

java.lang.Object
  dat1.TreeNode<K,V>

public class TreeNode<K extends java.lang.Comparable<? super K>,V>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a node in a BinaryTree. A TreeNode contains a lookup key and the value that is to be associated with it.

A BinaryTree retrieves a requested value by searching for the TreeNode containing the lookup key that was specified. It is the value of this TreeNode, if found, that is returned.

Author:
K. Atas
